handles inputs from the user interface
talks to the model and based on the input given, sends that requested data to the model.
    -let's say we move the player 1 pixel by using the joystick.
    -that input data should be relayed to the player model that the player has moved 1 pixel and
    increment the player position in the controller
    -then we will render the player object on the screen.
have methods to handle information generated by the user interface
